topic.title: Anesthesia Section2 - conformance rules

section.p: The Anesthesia Section records the type of anesthesia (e.g., general or local) and may state the actual agent used. This may be a subsection of the Procedure Description Section. The full details of anesthesia are usually found in a separate Anesthesia Note.
